{"article_id":"8OjwvRjjpieceJUc","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Federal officials","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"who examined school safety in the wake of the Parkland high school massacre","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"concluded","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that a top recommendation","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to prevent mass shootings","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"is to rescind policies","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"protecting black and other minority students from being disciplined at disproportionate rates .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The Federal Commission on School Safety","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"- formed","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"after 17 people were killed at Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School in Florida -","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"was tasked with evaluating best practices","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"to keep schools safe","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"and compiling its recommendations in a report .","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"The nearly 200-page report looked at various aspects of school safety","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"- including expanding mental health care -","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"and largely avoided the issue of guns ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"claiming","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"most school shooters get firearms from family members","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"and not by purchasing them .","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"The report does not make any recommendations","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"on changing state or federal gun laws","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and does not directly recommend arming teachers .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Instead , it offers guidelines","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"on arming `` highly trained school personnel ''","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"if a school chooses to do so , particularly in rural areas","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"where police officers are miles away from campuses","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"and can take longer to respond . `","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"` Through the Commission 's work , it has become even clearer","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"there is no single policy","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"that will make our schools safer .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"What will work for schools in Montana will be different than what will work for schools in Manhattan , ''","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Secretary of Education Betsy DeVos said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"An administration official told reporters on Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"that the report recommends rescinding the existing discipline guidance","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"because `` the commission was concerned with ... the recurring narrative","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that students were afraid","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"because individuals","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"who had a history of anti-social or in some instances aggressive behavior","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"were left unpunished . ''","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"The existing guidance ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"issued by the Department of Education and the Department of Justice in 2014 , under then-president Barack Obama ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"alerted school districts","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that they could be in violation of civil rights","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"if minority students were disciplined ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"including being suspended or expelled ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"at higher rates than white students .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"The deadliest school shootings in recent history have been committed by white students .","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"The Broward County School District in Florida started a program in 2013","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"- prior to the Obama administration guidance -","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"that aimed to reduce the number of times","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"students were referred to police ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"after data showed","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"the district had the highest arrest rates in the state ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"and black students were disproportionately ending up in handcuffs .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"The program sent kids to alternative education settings","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"designed to provide increased mentoring and intervention","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"to correct their behavior .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"The student","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"charged in the Stoneman Douglas massacre","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"was referred to the program in 2013","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"when he was in middle school","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"for vandalism ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"but he never attended .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"He had an extensive list of school infractions","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"ranging from 2012 to 2017 ,","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"resulting in multiple suspensions , detentions , and temporary bans from the school bus .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"An administration official told reporters Tuesday morning","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"that the report recommends","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"that schools review the security of their infrastructure","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"- including windows , hallways , and doors -","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"and , in some instances , have someone on school grounds","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"armed with a firearm ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"who would collaborate with law enforcement .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"The official said","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"the report encourages more coordination between schools and local law enforcement ,","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"adding","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"that some communities may benefit from hiring military veterans or retired law enforcement officers into school roles .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"The report also includes recommendations","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"aimed at reporters ,","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"news outlets should `` be more responsible in how they cover '' school shootings","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"and should not publish pictures of the perpetrator .","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"The commission also recommended ensuring that students have better access to mental health services at school ,","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"enhancing social and emotional learning for students ,","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"and also suggested","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"that states consider adopting `` extreme risk protection orders ''","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"that would temporarily withhold guns from those","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"who post a risk to themselves or others .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"On Tuesday afternoon president Trump hosted the commissioners as well as people affected by school shootings at the White House","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"and called the report `` a very important thing . ''","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"`` Nothing is more important","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"than protecting our nation 's children , ''","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Andy Pollack ,","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"whose daughter Meadow died in Parkland ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"called the report `` the most comprehensive report by any administration on a school shooting . ''","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"`` This is a huge step","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"towards making our schools safe for our country , ''","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Lori Alhadeff , the mother of 14-year-old Parkland victim , Alyssa , told Tuesday morning , in response to the commission 's findings .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"Fred Guttenberg ,","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"whose daughter Jaime Guttenberg , 14 , was killed in Parkland","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"told","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"that the work","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"survivors of the Marjorie Stoneman Douglas shooting have done so far really contributed to the quality of the report .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"But ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"`` this commission","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"by refusing to consider the role of guns in these incidents of gun violence ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"was missing the most critical piece , ''","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Guttenberg told Tuesday .","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"`` It is my hope that in the days and months ahead that this administration will change course","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"and work with me on the issue of gun safety , ''","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"`` Only then , will this be a school safety report","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"that I can fully embrace . ''","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"Mark Barden","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"whose son Daniel was one of the 20 first-graders","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"killed at Sandy Hook Elementary School in Newtown","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"issued a statement","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"that the report correctly points to the need","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"for all students to have access to mental health ersources .","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"`` While we agree with several of the recommendations ,","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"we are deeply concerned with the Department ' s continued support","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"for putting more firearms in our schools , ''","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":126,"text":"`` We believe","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"that teachers and school administrators should be focused on education , not weapons training .","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"Much more bipartisan work and leadership is needed from this White House and the new Congress","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"to save lives","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"and protect our children . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":261,"left":218,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":218,"left":19